ScriptLine.Text: Khǐ thayû̌ daô theingǎ nathû̌ bakyadò khǐ rwǎn ma dô̌ nathû̌ ngǎ cwaǐmǎ, dô̌ Wein Lò̌dikǐphao ngǎ dò pra cô̌ usûba khǐ lakhan lakhan ngǎ cwaǐmǎ arîkaǐ.
ScriptLine.Heading: false

ScriptLine.Text: Khǐ rwǎn ma cwaǐdò nathû̌ thá ka nî̌ba tamamo, ka aòbloncǔ dò tabathá, ka aòbábwaǐ dò tanāpau byan raò́ cwaǐdò ka theingǎ byan Bweca ta-aòhu aòbî mè mwaǐ Khrī.
ScriptLine.Heading: false
